\]
where \(d\) is a smooth positive function which coincides with \(\mathrm{dist}(x,\partial\Omega)\) near \(\partial\Omega\), and \(\partial^l\) denotes any partial differential operator of order \(l\).</p>},
	funding		= {NSF Grant DMS 0802958}
}

